ils, R.L.M., de Haan, M.H.A., Hemmer, J.G.A., van den Pol-van Dasselaar, A., de Boer, J.A., Evers, A.G., Holshof, G., Zom, R.L.G., DairyWise, a whole-farm dairy model (2007) J Dairy Sci, 90, pp. 5334-5346; Schils, R.L.M., Olesen, J.E., del Prado, A., Soussana, J.F., A review of farm level modelling approaches for mitigating greenhouse gas emissions from ruminant livestock systems (2007) Livest Sci, 112, pp. 240-251; Shindell, D.T., Faluvegi, G., Koch, D.M., Schmidt, G.A., Unger, N., Bauer, S.E., Improved attribution of climate forcing to emissions (2009) Science, 326, pp. 716-718; Six, J., Ogle, S.M., Breidt, F.J., Conant, R.T., Mosier, A.R., Paustian, K., The potential to mitigate global warming with no-tillage management is only realized when practised in the long term (2004) Glob Change Biol, 10, pp. 155-160; Smink, W., Pelikaan, W.F., van der Kolk, L.J., van Der Hoek, K.W., (2004) Methane production as a result from rumen fermentation in cattle calculated bij using IPCCTier 2 method; Smith, P., Land use change and soil organic carbon dynamics (2008) Nutr Cycl Agroecosyst, 81, pp. 169-178; Smith, W.N., Grant, B.B., Desjardins, R.L., Worth, D., Li, C., Boles, S.H., Huffman, E.C., A tool to link agricultural activity data with the DNDC model to estimate GHG emission factors in Canada (2010) Agric Ecosyst Environ, 136, pp. 301-309; Soussana, J.F., Allard, V., Pilegaard, K., Ambus, P., Amman, C., Campbell, C., Ceschia, E., Valentini, R., Full accounting of the greenhouse gas (CO2, N2O, CH4) budget of nine European grassland sites (2007) Agric Ecosyst Environ, 121, pp. 121-134; Steinfeld, H., Gerber, P., Wassenaar, T., Castel, V., Rosales, M., de Haan, C., (2006) Livestock's Long Shadow, Environmental Issues and Options, p. 390. , Rome: Food and Agricultural Organisation; Stewart, C.E., Paustian, K., Conant, R.T., Plante, A.F., Six, J., Soil carbon saturation: concept, evidence and evaluation (2007) Biogeochemistry, 86, pp. 19-31; van Der Hoek, K.W., van Schijndel, M.